'use strict';

module.exports = {
  SLEEP: 0x00, // deprecated
  QUIT: 0x01,
  INIT_DB: 0x02,
  QUERY: 0x03,
  FIELD_LIST: 0x04,
  CREATE_DB: 0x05,
  DROP_DB: 0x06,
  REFRESH: 0x07,
  SHUTDOWN: 0x08,
  STATISTICS: 0x09,
  PROCESS_INFO: 0x0a, // deprecated
  CONNECT: 0x0b, // deprecated
  PROCESS_KILL: 0x0c,
  DEBUG: 0x0d,
  PING: 0x0e,
  TIME: 0x0f, // deprecated
  DELAYED_INSERT: 0x10, // deprecated
  CHANGE_USER: 0x11,
  BINLOG_DUMP: 0x12,
  TABLE_DUMP: 0x13,
  CONNECT_OUT: 0x14,
  REGISTER_SLAVE: 0x15,
  STMT_PREPARE: 0x16,
  STMT_EXECUTE: 0x17,
  STMT_SEND_LONG_DATA: 0x18,
  STMT_CLOSE: 0x19,
  STMT_RESET: 0x1a,
  SET_OPTION: 0x1b,
  STMT_FETCH: 0x1c,
  DAEMON: 0x1d, // deprecated
  BINLOG_DUMP_GTID: 0x1e,
  UNKNOWN: 0xff // bad!
};
